on star- black hole and binary black hole systems are 1.3 x\n10^{-4}, 3.1 x 10^{-5} and 6.4 x 10^{-6} Mpc^{-3}yr^{-1}, respectively. These\nupper limits are up to a factor 1.4 lower than previously derived limits. We\nalso report on results from a blind injection challenge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2011 20:49:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2011 19:42:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Dec 2011 20:18:59 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2012 17:41:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-27"}
