est that sufficient radial velocity precision can be achieved\nfor at least a subset of slowly rotating young stars to search for hot Jupiter\nplanets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2011 21:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Feb 2012 05:54:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
