y on the amplitudes revealed from observational data and the\noccurrence of the dichotomy also derived from phenomenological data have to be\nconfirmed by appropriate theoretical models of stellar structure and pulsation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2011 09:04:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-13"}
