ommend its application to a larger sample covering lower as well as\nhigher metallicities. Further prospects of the method include abundance\ndeterminations for individual elements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2011 11:32:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
